details: Switch up your off-duty style with this juniors' Tech Fleece Hoodie from Nike. In a Dark Heather Grey colourway, this standard-fit hoodie uses Nike's innovative Tech Fleece fabric, which offers warmth without the weight. name: ADIDAS SPRT COLLECTION MW TRACK JACKET

The seersucker material stands out with 3-Stripes pinstripes, plus a flash of the classic signoff down the sleeves in contrast color.

name: BANANA REPUBLIC Slim LUXE Traveler Jean
details: Incredibly soft and smooth, our lightweight LUXE Traveler Denim has an extra-fine weave and is engineered with added stretch for extra mobility. Plus, it has a brushed interior (like your favorite sweatshirt) for first-class comfort. You asked for it and it's finally here! We updated our Slim fit by taking in the leg from knee to hem for a slightly slimmer fit. Traditional five-pocket styling. Zip fly with button closure. Belt loops. *Our denim is made under strict guidelines to ensure that the water used in washing and dyeing is safe and clean before it is released into the environment. Produced in a facility that runs P.A.C.E. – Gap Inc.'s program to educate and empower women in the communities where our products are made.
